column2: SELECT m.Name AS Name_cls, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra, o.dec AS dec, o.modelMag_u as mu, o.modelMag_g as mg, o.modelMag_r as mr, o.modelMag_i as mi, o.modelMag_z as mz, c.z as photoZ, c.zErr as photoZErr, IS# (s.z, #) as z, IS# (s.zErr, #) as zErr into mydb.maughan_SDSS_gals_fov from Galaxy as o left outer join SpecObj as s on o.objID = s.bestObjID join dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq (m.Xra, m.Xdec, m.theta7Mpc) as n on n.objID = o.objID join Photoz as c on c.objID = o.objID WHERE c.z > # AND clean = # AND (calibStatus_r & #) ! = #
